## 🚀 How to Run in Google Colab

**Step 1** — Open [colab.research.google.com](https://colab.research.google.com), create a new notebook

**Step 2** — Upload the file OR copy-paste all code into one cell

**Step 3** — Run it. It auto-installs all packages, then asks you:

```
👥 How many agents do you want in the swarm? (min 3, max 30): 15
📈 Enter Indian stock ticker (e.g. RELIANCE.NS / TCS.NS / INFY.NS): RELIANCE.NS
🌐 Paste a news URL for live sentiment (or press Enter to skip): https://economictimes.com/...
🔁 How many debate rounds? (1–6, default 3): 4
```

