## 🤖 10 Agent Archetypes (auto-scaled to your number)

| Agent | What they do |
|---|---|
| Momentum Trader | RSI + MACD + Moving average crossovers |
| Contrarian | Fades crowd, buys extreme dips |
| Fundamentalist | P/E, P/B, EPS growth, dividend yield |
| Quant/Algo | All 7 signals weighted linearly |
| Sentiment Analyst | Scrapes your URL + news mood |
| Risk Manager | Volatility + beta dampener |
| Technical Analyst | Golden cross, 52-week position |
| Macro/Sector | Sector rotation, market cap tier |
| Value-Trap Detector | Warns when cheap stocks are traps |
| Breakout Hunter | Volume spikes above 50-DMA |

If you pick 20 agents, it cycles all 10 types twice with different names.

---

## 📊 What the Output Shows

- **Live NSE/BSE data** via `yfinance` (real price, P/E, RSI, MACD etc.)
- **Each agent's reasoning** every round with confidence bar
- **URL sentiment** blended in if you provide a link (Economic Times, Moneycontrol etc.)
- **Final prediction**: `🚀 STRONG BUY / 📈 BUY / 🤝 HOLD / 📉 SELL / 🔻 STRONG SELL`
- **Price target estimate** + stop loss level
- **Score evolution table** across all rounds
